lyrics:
[verse]
Today is a special day, it's Nadya's birthday
Let's celebrate and make it the best in every way
With laughter and joy, let's sing a sweet melody
Gathering together, creating memories so heavenly

[chorus]
Happy Birthday to Nadya, our shining star
May your dreams come true, no matter how far
We raise our glasses, toast to your happiness
Wishing you love and success, endless and limitless
